{"title":"世界语","authors":["袁水拍"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":10,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁水拍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小跳蚤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见人咬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬到南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南遭难；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬到北，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北倒霉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬到东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉普车直冲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬到西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"间谍特务一大批，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的披上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的不披“和平队”的皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬看中你的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼变成他的军事基地；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬看中你的名胜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼变成酒排间、阿飞舞中心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬看中科学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学变成了瘟疫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬看中的文人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连皮带骨出卖干净；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国佬看中缪斯，〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缪斯变成娼妓；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看中佛像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍了脑袋装箱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“美国佬，滚回去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——最流行的世界语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕美国兵在巴黎塞尚墓前的恶劣行径，请见下图。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国大兵在巴黎"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}